      <title>位运算</title>
      <link href="2019/04/09/wei-yun-suan/"/>
      <url>2019/04/09/wei-yun-suan/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong><center>位运算符是在数字底层（即表示数字的32个数位）进行操作的。</center></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;">在学习位运算之前，要知道什么是原码、反码、补码，还有什么是机器数和真值。机器数是指一个数在计算机中的二进制表现形式，并且是含有符号的，最高位存放符号，0为正，1为负。因为机器数有符号位，所以机器数表现的值就不是它自身值。为了进行区分，就有了真值的概念，真值才是机器数的真正数值。比如十进制中的5，机器数是<code>0000 0101</code>，真值是<code>+5</code>；如果是-5，那么机器数就是<code>1000 0101</code>，真值为<code>-5</code>。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em;">原码、反码、补码是机器存储一个具体数字的编码方式。</p><h2 id="相关概念"><a href="#相关概念" class="headerlink" title="相关概念"></a>相关概念</h2><h3 id="机器数与真值"><a href="#机器数与真值" class="headerlink" title="机器数与真值"></a>机器数与真值</h3><p>机器数：是指一个数在计算机中的二进制表现形式，并且是含有符号的，最高位存放符号，0为正，1为负。<br>真值：机器数的真正数值。</p><h3 id="原码、反码与补码"><a href="#原码、反码与补码" class="headerlink" title="原码、反码与补码"></a>原码、反码与补码</h3><h4 id="原码"><a href="#原码" class="headerlink" title="原码"></a>原码</h4><p>原码就是机器数(符号位加上真值的绝对值)。第一位表示符号，其余位表示值。比如：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">+1 &#x3D; [原码]0000 0001；-1 &#x3D; [原码]1000 0001。<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="反码"><a href="#反码" class="headerlink" title="反码"></a>反码</h4><p>反码的表示方式：正数的反码与原码相同；负数的反码符号位不变其余取反。比如：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">+1 &#x3D; [原码]0000 0001 &#x3D; [反码]0000 0001；-1 &#x3D; [原码]1000 0001 &#x3D; [反码]1111 1110。<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="补码"><a href="#补码" class="headerlink" title="补码"></a>补码</h4><p>补码：正数的补码与原码相同；负数的补码符号位不变，其余按位取反后+1。比如：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">+1 &#x3D; [原码]0000 0001 &#x3D; [反码]0000 0001 &#x3D; [补码]0000 0001；-1 &#x3D; [原码]1000 0001 &#x3D; [反码]1111 1110 &#x3D; [补码]1111 1111。<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="位运算的算法"><a href="#位运算的算法" class="headerlink" title="位运算的算法"></a>位运算的算法</h2><h3 id="按位与（-amp-）"><a href="#按位与（-amp-）" class="headerlink" title="按位与（&amp;）"></a>按位与（&amp;）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment">// 按位与（&amp;）: 两个1为1</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> <span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 0011 &amp; 0110 = 0010 = 2</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="按位或（-）"><a href="#按位或（-）" class="headerlink" title="按位或（|）"></a>按位或（|）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment">// 按位或（|）: 一个1即为1</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 0011 | 1000 = 1011 = 11</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="按位异或（-）"><a href="#按位异或（-）" class="headerlink" title="按位异或（^）"></a>按位异或（^）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment">// 按位异或（^）: 相反为1</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span> <span class="token operator">^</span> <span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 0010 ^ 0110 = 0100 = 4</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="按位取反（-）"><a href="#按位取反（-）" class="headerlink" title="按位取反（~）"></a>按位取反（~）</h3><p>是对补码进行了取反<br>补码 &gt; 取反 &gt; 补码 = 原码；也可以用此公式计算<code>~x = -(x+1)</code>;</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">~</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// ~0000 0100 > 0000 0100[补码] > 1111 1011[取反] > 1000 0101[补码] = -5</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">~</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// ~1000 0100 > 1111 1100[补码] > 0000 0011 > 0000 0011 = 3</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="按位左移（-lt-lt-）"><a href="#按位左移（-lt-lt-）" class="headerlink" title="按位左移（&lt;&lt;）"></a>按位左移（&lt;&lt;）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment">// 按位左移（&lt;&lt;）: 向左移一位</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token operator">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 00000110 &lt;&lt; 2 = 00011000 = 24</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="按位右移（-gt-gt-）"><a href="#按位右移（-gt-gt-）" class="headerlink" title="按位右移（&gt;&gt;）"></a>按位右移（&gt;&gt;）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment">// 按位右移（>>）: 向右移一位</span><span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token operator">>></span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 0110 >> 1 = 0011 = 3</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="位运算的用处"><a href="#位运算的用处" class="headerlink" title="位运算的用处"></a>位运算的用处</h2><h3 id="求奇偶性"><a href="#求奇偶性" class="headerlink" title="求奇偶性"></a>求奇偶性</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">judgeParity</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> a<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> result <span class="token operator">=</span> a <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>result <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>        <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"为偶数"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span> <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>        <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"为奇数"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="两个数交换位置"><a href="#两个数交换位置" class="headerlink" title="两个数交换位置"></a>两个数交换位置</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">exchangeNum</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> a<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"a:"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> a <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"\t"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"b:"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    a <span class="token operator">=</span> a <span class="token operator">^</span> b<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">/* 0010 ^ 0110 = 0100a = 4 */</span>    b <span class="token operator">=</span> b <span class="token operator">^</span> a<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">/* 0110 ^ 0100 = 0010b = 2 */</span>    a <span class="token operator">=</span> a <span class="token operator">^</span> b<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">/* 0100 ^ 0110 = 0110a = 6 */</span>    <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"a:"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> a <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"\t"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"b:"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="两个数的平均数"><a href="#两个数的平均数" class="headerlink" title="两个数的平均数"></a>两个数的平均数</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">averageNum</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> a<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> average <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>a <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a <span class="token operator">^</span> b<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">>></span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"average:"</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> average<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
